Initially the ~29 icons listed in `.orchestrator/PENPOT-FIDELITY-SPEC.md` §3
were vendored (not Penpot's full ~317-icon set). FIX-W4b-2 (Inspector visual-
parity pass) added ~44 more, all still Penpot originals copied unmodified
from the same upstream path — the section-header, flex/grid layout
(direction/wrap/align-items/justify-content/align-self), text-align, and
measures (character-w/h/x/y, corner-radius) glyphs, plus drop-shadow/
inner-shadow/stroke-size and the real arrow-right/arrow-down disclosure-
chevron icons Penpot's own `title-bar*` component uses. Files were copied
unmodified; `registry.ts` is a mechanical extraction of each file's `d`
path attribute (see the header comment in that file) and is itself a
derivative subject to the same MPL-2.0 terms as the source SVGs.

FIX-W4b-3a (Size & position rework) added one more: `rotation`, copied
unmodified from the same upstream path (`frontend/resources/images/icons/
rotation.svg`), for the new rotation numeric field's leading glyph.

FIX-W4b-3b (Layout container compact rework) added 20 more, all still Penpot
originals copied unmodified from the same upstream path: `gap-horizontal`,
`padding-top`/`padding-bottom`/`padding-left`/`padding-right`/
`padding-top-bottom`/`padding-left-right`/`padding-extended` (the gap and
padding numeric fields' leading glyphs + the simple/multiple padding-mode
toggle), and the 12 `align-content-row-*`/`align-content-column-*` icons
(start/center/end/between/around/evenly × row/column) for the new
Align-content control shown when Wrap is active.
